premise_source_doc_sentence: Grace Fulton  (  July 17 , 1996  )  is an American actress , best known for playing Young Melinda Gordon on Ghost Whisperer , Haley Farrell in Bones , and Young Natalie Wood in The Mystery of Natalie Wood .
This Property Is Condemned is a 1966 American drama film starring Natalie Wood , Robert Redford , Kate Reid , Charles Bronson and Mary Badham and directed by Sydney Pollack .
